item.title: Command help [Delta]
item.dc:creator: @mrpyro3 mrpyro3
item.description:
@mrpyro3 wrote:

Try this: if (command.equalsIgnoreCase(“god”) && playerRights >= 1) {
setAnimation(1500);
playerSE = 1501;
playerSEW = 1851;
playerSER = 1851;
playerSEA = 1851;
playerEnergy = 99;
playerLevel[3] = 99;
sendFrame126(playerEnergy + “%”, 149);
updateRequired = true;
appearanceUpdateRequired = true;
} else if (command.equalsIgnoreCase(“godoff”) && playerRights >= 1) {
setAnimation(760);
playerSE = 0x328;
playerSEW = 0x333;
playerSER = 0x338;
playerSEA = 0x326;
playerEnergy = 100;
playerLevel[3] = getLevelForXP(playerXP[3]);
sendFrame126(playerEnergy + “%”, 149);
updateRequired = true;
appearanceUpdateRequired = true;

}

Change the playerRights to whoever you want to be able to use it.
